# ASTRA_ Git Ignore Rules
# See AGENTS.md Section 16 for rationale.

# ── Rust build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────
/target/

# ── Secrets (NEVER commit) ────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*

# ── OS and editor files ───────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Local AI agent configuration ─────────────────────────────
# These files contain machine-specific AI agent guidance and
# are not intended for version control.
/AGENTS.md
/CLAUDE.md

# ── Local planning and design documents ───────────────────────
# Entire docs/ directory is local until individual documents are
# explicitly ready for version control. To track a specific doc,
# use: git add -f docs/my-document.md
/docs/

# ── Python (future-proofing for Issue #11) ────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
*.egg
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/
dist/
build/
*.whl

# ── Coverage artifacts ────────────────────────────────────────
lcov.info
*.lcov
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
